(define/contract (sum-distance nums s d)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) string? exact-integer? exact-integer?)
  (define mod 1000000007)
  (define (direction c) (if (eq? c #\L) -1 1))
  (define (mod-add x y) (modulo (+ x y) mod))
  (define (mod-abs x) (modulo (abs x) mod))
  
  (define moves (map direction (string->list s)))
  (define positions (map + nums (map * moves (make-list (length nums) d))))
  
  (define (sum-distances lst)
    (let loop ([i 0] [acc 0])
      (if (= i (length lst))
          acc
          (loop (+ i 1) (foldl (lambda (elem sum) (mod-add sum (mod-abs (- elem (list-ref lst i))))) acc (drop lst (+ i 1)))))))
  
  (sum-distances (sort positions <)))
